Select To Speak
================================================================================
Select To Speak reads selected text on a webpage. Simply click and drag your mouse over a portion of a webpage. After selecting, tap the Control key to hear the text read aloud with text to speech.


Installation
================================================================================
- go to chrome://extensions
- click the "Load unpacked extension" button.
- navigate to the directory containing this file.
- click ok.

Features
================================================================================
- make a selection with the mouse (or keyboard) and tap to read
- mouse the mouse around the page and hear the type of item under your mouse


